sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as DSP API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>pod-to-pod TLS
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>8001/TCP HTTP<br/>pod-to-pod TLS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Pod as Pipeline Pod
    participant S3 as Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>pod-to-pod TLS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>pod-to-pod TLS
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission via Dashboard

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward HTTPS (Reencrypt)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    OAuth->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: INSERT pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL over TLS<br/>Auth: DB Password
    DB-->>API: ACK
    API->>WFC: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTP/8001 pod-to-pod TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    WFC->>K8s: Create Workflow Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Workflow Created
    WFC-->>API: Workflow Scheduled
    API-->>OAuth: 201 Created
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over Pod,DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution

    K8s->>Pod: Start Pipeline Pod
    Pod->>API: Get Pipeline Spec<br/>HTTP/8888 pod-to-pod TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>Pod: Pipeline Definition
    Pod->>S3: Download Input Data<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: S3 Credentials
    S3-->>Pod: Input Data
    Pod->>Pod: Execute Pipeline Step
    Pod->>MLMD: Record Artifact Metadata<br/>gRPC/8080 pod-to-pod TLS<br/>Auth: mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: Store Lineage<br/>MySQL/3306 pod-to-pod TLS<br/>Auth: DB Password
    Pod->>S3: Upload Output Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: S3 Credentials
    S3-->>Pod: Upload Complete
    Pod->>API: Update Run Status<br/>HTTP/8888 pod-to-pod TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over PA,DB: Flow 3: Workflow State Persistence

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow State Change
    PA->>API: Update Run in DB<br/>gRPC/8887 pod-to-pod TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    API->>DB: UPDATE run status<br/>MySQL/3306 pod-to-pod TLS<br/>Auth: DB Password
    DB-->>API: ACK
    API-->>PA: Sync Complete

    Note over User,DB: Flow 4: Artifact Retrieval

    User->>Route: GET /apis/v2beta1/artifacts/{id}<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward HTTPS (Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>API: GET /artifacts/{id}<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: SELECT artifact metadata<br/>MySQL/3306 pod-to-pod TLS
    DB-->>API: Artifact Location
    API->>S3: Generate Signed URL<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    API-->>OAuth: Redirect to Signed URL
    OAuth-->>Route: Redirect
    Route-->>User: Redirect to S3
    User->>S3: GET artifact<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Signed URL
    S3-->>User: Artifact Data
